    "description": "UPC++ is a C++ library that supports Partitioned Global Address Space\n(PGAS) programming, and is designed to interoperate smoothly and\nefficiently with MPI, OpenMP, CUDA, ROCm/HIP and AMTs. It leverages\nGASNet-EX to deliver low-overhead, fine-grained communication, including\nRemote Memory Access (RMA) and Remote Procedure Call (RPC).\n",
    "homepage": "https://upcxx.lbl.gov",
